parameters: Lala: I won't let you escape this time!!

Remiel: Hehe, you're quite spirited,
aren't you?♪

Remiel: Eden-sama had foretold it,
didn't he?

Remiel: You all are aiming for this
sanctuary.

Zerachiel: So they even prepared a
giant...

Lala: Huh? Despite the prophecy, don't
you have a lack of fighting power?

Remiel: Dealing with you all is enough
for little old me, Remi-chan.

Lala: Even though you lost last time,
you sure talk big.

Remiel: Hehe, I'll let you know if you
can defeat me ♥

Remiel: I am Remiel, the trusted
confidant of Archangel Sariel... I have
come.
